{"tid":1350772,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一整代人賣港，到今日燒到春袋就懺悔","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:29.000Z","uid":238013,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"197fe4e4f6fc6b9502b858b9082ad87e0bbd7534","tid":1350772,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190722/59850202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59850202&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=667a6291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59850202&h=62b25718\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190722/59850202</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">肥媽不停哭訴要求林鄭出來：「我真係唔想離開香港呀</span>，我唔想一家人走散晒，我好辛苦呀，已經食一種藥壓抑自己，而家唔夠，要食夠兩種藥，日日咁喊，我頂唔順！唔該你哋叫林太，叫啲大人，讀得書多嘅人出嚟講吓嘢啦，出嚟主持公道，我又唔識法律，又唔識乜係啱乜係錯，我唔想走呀，屋企人叫我離開香港，我真係唔想走，嗚嗚嗚，我求下你哋，出嚟同兩邊講吓嘢啦，我唔識字唔知點算唔識解決，我唔想走，唔想移民，唔想離開香港，唔該你叫佢哋出嚟講吓嘢，抒緩而家咁嘅環境呀。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讚大灣區，食魚生嗰陣唔見你咁講？<br />\n<br />\n中國咁好你唔返去住？</span><br />\n<br />\n著數你哋拎盡，苦你哋就唔捱， 可能威脅到你哋利益就打壓，今日燒到埋身知痛啦咩？"},{"pid":"893aec6628c69002f3e1dacfc0c6b6e49f90d596","tid":1350772,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"現眼報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}